<plot>"Installation of Love" is a bizarre and crazy satire constructed as a film in a film in a film. For her first feature film "Guardian of the Frontier", Maja Weiss, the director and co-writer won Manfred Salzgeber award for the most innovative European film at Berlinale 2002. "Installation of Love" is also a unique project concerning the story telling even though that the main plot of the film is conventional and universal. It is a search for love, or how to rediscover or re-install love in your life - love in its widest sense.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?266489</url></doc>
